  .guide
    .content
      h2 Production
      p The flag should have a proportion of 3:5. So if the flag has a hoist of 3 feet, its fly should be 5 feet.
      p If resized, it must maintain these proportions.
    .visual
      img(src='/assets/images/flag-illinois-dimensions.svg')

  .guide
    .content
      h2 Previous iteration
      p The Lucy Derwent version of the flag was used from 1915-1969 and featured selected imagery from the state seal.
    .visual.flag
